description:
Comedian Jack Whitehall (CLIFFORD, TRAVELS WITH MY FATHER) is fresh off Netflix’s JONAS BROTHERS FAMILY ROAST and on GOOD FOR YOU talking to Whitney about dating British guys, the nostril to butthole size ratio, and Johnny Depp. Whitney also considers becoming Jack’s celebrity stalker.
